<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-09-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-09-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="67" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d67">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-09-22"><hi rend="italic">September 22,
                                    1894</hi></date>. (Received Sept. 24.)</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Minister for foreign affairs officially informs me that it is the
                            intention of the President to terminate reciprocity treaty on January 1
                            proximo.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>